Deployment/Configuration Mgmt. Software: Puppet, Terraform, Bicep, Helmchart, Ansible;
Scripting: Bash, Python, Powershell, Ruby;
Tools: Git, OpenSSL, tcpdump, Wireshark, PowerCLI, Sysinternals Suite




Soft Skills

Continuous learner;
Time management;
Interpersonal skills;
Teamwork.




